# 🎯 Why Learn C?

Learning C provides a strong foundation for programming.

Benefits include:

- Understand how computers manage memory
- Learn pointers and memory addresses
- Improve problem-solving skills
- Build efficient software
- Prepare for system programming
- Develop embedded systems
- Strengthen understanding of data structures and algorithms

